# Layout System Rules

## Component Hierarchy

```
Layout          # Page shell (sidebar, marketing, admin)
  └── Page      # Full page content for a route
       └── Block    # Group of components (e.g., HeroBlock, PricingBlock)
            └── Component  # Atomic UI pieces (Button, Card, Input)
```

| Level | What it is | Examples |
|-------|-----------|----------|
| **Layout** | Page shell with navigation structure | `AppSidebarLayout`, `MarketingLayout`, `AdminLayout` |
| **Page** | Full page assembled from blocks | `DashboardPage`, `PricingPage`, `SettingsPage` |
| **Block** | Reusable section/group of components | `HeroBlock`, `PricingTableBlock`, `DataTableBlock` |
| **Component** | Atomic UI element | `Button`, `Card`, `Input`, `Avatar` (shadcn/ui) |

## Reuse Priority

**ALWAYS follow this order when building UI:**

1. **Check `components/ui/`** - Use existing shadcn/ui components first
2. **Install from shadcn registry** - If component doesn't exist: `npx shadcn@latest add [component]`
3. **Create component** - Only if nothing suitable exists in shadcn
4. **Check `components/blocks/`** - Reuse existing blocks for common patterns
5. **Create block** - Only if no suitable block exists
6. **Check existing pages** - See if similar page already exists to copy from
7. **Create page** - Only if truly new page type
8. **Use existing layout** - Pick from available layouts (see below)
9. **Create layout** - VERY RARE - Only for fundamentally new page structures

## Available Layouts

### 1. App Sidebar Layout

**Visual Structure:**
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Header (app name, user menu)            │
├──────────┬──────────────────────────────┤
│          │                              │
│ Sidebar  │     Main Content             │
│          │                              │
│ ┌──────┐ │                              │
│ │Group │ │                              │
│ │ Link │ │                              │
│ │ Link │ │                              │
│ └──────┘ │                              │
│ ┌──────┐ │                              │
│ │Group │ │                              │
│ │ Link │ │                              │
│ └──────┘ │                              │
│          │                              │
└──────────┴──────────────────────────────┘
```

**Characteristics:**
- Fixed header with app branding and user menu
- Left sidebar with grouped, collapsible navigation sections
- Sidebar toggleable on mobile
- Main content area scrolls independently
- Consistent across all authenticated app pages

**Use Cases:**
- Dashboard / home
- Settings pages
- Data tables / lists
- Detail/edit pages
- User profile
- Any authenticated app experience

**Location:** `components/layouts/app-sidebar/`
**Route Group:** `app/(app)/`

### 2. Marketing Layout

**Visual Structure:**
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Header (transparent → solid on scroll)  │
│ Logo        Nav Links        CTA Button │
├─────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                         │
│           Main Content                  │
│                                         │
├─────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Footer (multi-column)                   │
│ Product | Company | Resources | Legal   │
│         © 2025 Company Name             │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Characteristics:**
- Header starts transparent over hero content
- Header becomes solid/blurred on scroll
- Navigation links with optional CTA button
- Multi-column footer with organized link sections
- No sidebar - full-width content area

**Use Cases:**
- Landing page / homepage
- About / Team
- Pricing
- Features / Product pages
- Blog / articles
- Contact
- Legal (Privacy, Terms)

**Location:** `components/layouts/marketing/`
**Route Group:** `app/(marketing)/`

### 3. Admin Layout

**Existing layout - unchanged**
- Located in `app/admin/`
- Used for admin dashboard pages
- Protected by admin role checks

## Layout Selection Table

| Page Type | Layout | Route Group |
|-----------|--------|-------------|
| Dashboard | App Sidebar | `(app)/` |
| Settings | App Sidebar | `(app)/` |
| Data tables | App Sidebar | `(app)/` |
| User profile (in-app) | App Sidebar | `(app)/` |
| Analytics | App Sidebar | `(app)/` |
| Landing page | Marketing | `(marketing)/` |
| About/Team | Marketing | `(marketing)/` |
| Pricing (public) | Marketing | `(marketing)/` |
| Features | Marketing | `(marketing)/` |
| Blog | Marketing | `(marketing)/` |
